  "Aqua Roma": "Aqua Roma W26: 194 bookings on ~5658 attributed users (pagePath aquanyc), CVR ~3.4%. Combined Aqua NYC is +14.7% YoY (211 vs 184 LY) but \u221228.5% WoW as demand eased into the July 4th holiday. Meta held efficient at $29.5/schedule (103 sched); Google normalised to $811 spend / 24 conv after last week's summer-Search surge.",
